 to finance working capital and improvements to dealership facilities to finance the purchase of dealership real estate and to finance other dealer vehicle programs in addition it offers various insurance products and services including physical damage insurance coverage for vehicles at dealer locations and vehicles in transit between final assembly plants and dealer locations and contractual liability insurance on extended service contracts commercial automobile and general liability insurance and surety bonds further the company provides fordbranded insurance products that are underwritten by nonaffiliated insurance companies the company was founded in  and is headquartered in dearborn michigan ford motor credit company llc is a subsidiary of ford holdings llc detailed description one american roaddearborn mi united statesfounded in  employees phone  wwwcreditfordcom key executives for ford motor credit company llc ms nancy joy falotico chairman and chief executive officer age  mr marion b harris chief financial officer treasurer and director age  mr thomas charles schneider chief risk officer executive vice president and director david j witten assistant secretary ms susan j thomas associate general counsel compensation as of fiscal year  ford motor credit company llc key developments ford motor credit company llc to report q  results on jul   jul   ford motor credit company llc announced that they will report q  results at  am us eastern standard time on jul   ford motor credit company llc issues and sells  aggregate principal amount of  notes due june   jun   ford motor credit company llc issued and sold  aggregate principal amount of  notes due june   and  aggregate principal amount of floating rate notes due june   the debt securities are to be issued pursuant to the provisions of an indenture dated as of march   the indenture between the company and the bank of new york mellon as trustee pursuant to the terms of the indenture the company has created as a ser